# Copy to `.dev.vars` (git-ignored) for `npm run dev` (wrangler pages dev).
# These back the /api/intakes and /api/suppliers Pages Functions (Turso HTTP API).
# The Supplement Board tab is pure localStorage and needs NEITHER of these.
TURSO_URL="https://your-db-name.turso.io"
TURSO_TOKEN="your-turso-auth-token"
